{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/procreate-paintings/emil-i-portrait/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Watercolor, not watercolor","date":"2016-04-26T00:00:00.000Z","date_pretty":"April 26th, 2016","date_from_now":"4 years ago","last_modified_at":"2020-01-06T15:56:36.000Z","last_modified_at_from_now":"6 months ago","path":"/procreate-paintings/emil-i-portrait/","author":null,"excerpt":"Portrait of Emil I. digitally painted with Procreate on an iPad.","tags":["Procreate","portrait","illustration","Sktchy","time lapse"],"image":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"aspectRatio":0.7493188010899182,"src":"/static/9bd467e320f52776b8bfb08adf993a1f/fc20c/emil-i-procreate.jpg","srcSet":"/static/9bd467e320f52776b8bfb08adf993a1f/6e883/emil-i-procreate.jpg 275w,\n/static/9bd467e320f52776b8bfb08adf993a1f/a09ef/emil-i-procreate.jpg 550w,\n/static/9bd467e320f52776b8bfb08adf993a1f/fc20c/emil-i-procreate.jpg 1100w,\n/static/9bd467e320f52776b8bfb08adf993a1f/9352a/emil-i-procreate.jpg 1600w","sizes":"(max-width: 1100px) 100vw, 1100px"},"fixed":{"src":"/static/9bd467e320f52776b8bfb08adf993a1f/fc20c/emil-i-procreate.jpg","height":1466,"width":1100}}},"toc":null,"comments":null,"comments_locked":null,"hide_meta":null},"id":"9168c168-706d-56f4-9db0-d91bb9465bc1","html":"<p>Portrait of Emil I. inspired by a <a href=\"https://sktchy.com/TXmmCc\">photograph on Sktchy</a>. Digitally painted with Procreate on an iPad Air 2.</p>\n<p>When Adobe and Adonit released the <a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Adobe-Creative-Connected-Precision-Stylus/dp/B00LNECVN6/ref=as_li_ss_tl?ie=UTF8&#x26;linkCode=ll1&#x26;tag=mademist-20&#x26;linkId=643de6452764ad91cc2a8a8077f11204\">Ink &#x26; Slide</a> stylus and ruler combo I was intrigued. There really weren’t any well designed pressure sensitive styli out there with a fine tip. The high sticker price scared me away initially, after being burned by the <a href=\"/mastering-paper/pogo-connect-smart-pen/\">Pogo Connect</a> and its myriad of hardware issues — so I decided to wait.</p>\n<p>Fast forward to last week when bought an Adobe Ink that was on sale for 90% off. I could live with losing $20 if it turned out to be a dud…</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; background-color: var(--input-background-color); max-width: 900px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 61.09090909090909%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image lazyload\"\n        alt=\"Work in progress with the Adonit Ink stylus\"\n        title=\"Work in progress with the Adonit Ink stylus\"\n        data-src=\"/static/da92ef097f1519d7c3fd94b4e7dcc567/062c0/emil-i-procreate-adonit-ink-900.jpg\"\n        data-srcset=\"/static/da92ef097f1519d7c3fd94b4e7dcc567/16841/emil-i-procreate-adonit-ink-900.jpg 275w,\n/static/da92ef097f1519d7c3fd94b4e7dcc567/50c97/emil-i-procreate-adonit-ink-900.jpg 550w,\n/static/da92ef097f1519d7c3fd94b4e7dcc567/062c0/emil-i-procreate-adonit-ink-900.jpg 900w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p>Well after drawing with it for a few hours it definitely has some issues. Most of can be traced back to the <a href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20161231184219/http://www.adonit.net/blog/archives/2015/05/07/ipad-air-2-performance/\">iPad Air 2</a>, which doesn’t exactly support the stylus properly.</p>\n<p>There’s some serious lag which I can give it a pass on since this thing came out way before the Apple Pencil. That said, if you can get used to the lag it gets the job done.</p>\n<p>On the positive side, the tip is made of a hard plastic. Unlike styli that have the fat rubber nibs — it doesn’t appear it will ever wear out. Plus it doesn’t smear grease all over the screen which is a big win in my book.</p>\n<p>After getting a taste at what pressure sensitive drawing with Procreate could be like, I just want to own the real thing — an <a href=\"/articles/ipad-pro/\">Apple Pencil and iPad Pro</a>.</p>\n<p>Time lapse video recorded within Procreate.</p>\n<p><div class=\"gatsby-resp-iframe-wrapper\" style=\"padding-bottom: 56.42857142857143%; position: relative; height: 0; overflow: hidden; \" > <div class=\"embedVideo-container\"> <iframe data-src=\"https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/fFX1CUO472U?rel=0\" class=\"embedVideo-iframe lazyload\" style=\"border:0; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%; \" allowfullscreen></iframe> </div> </div></p>\n<p><strong>Tools used:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Adobe-Creative-Connected-Precision-Stylus/dp/B00LNECVN6/ref=as_li_ss_tl?ie=UTF8&#x26;qid=1461688574&#x26;sr=8-1&#x26;keywords=adobe+ink&#x26;linkCode=ll1&#x26;tag=mademist-20&#x26;linkId=85c30649adf50e2ff0b9c753f6dfe2c9\">Adobe Ink stylus</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/IPad_Air_2\">iPad Air 2</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://procreate.art/\">Procreate</a></li>\n</ul>","excerpt":"Portrait of Emil I. inspired by a photograph on Sktchy. Digitally painted with Procreate on an iPad Air 2. When Adobe and Adonit released…","timeToRead":2,"tableOfContents":""},"comments":{"edges":[]}},"pageContext":{"next":{"frontmatter":{"path":"/mastering-paper/switching-tools/","title":"Paper for iOS quick tip: switching tools","categories":["mastering-paper"],"tags":["Paper for iOS","Apple","tutorial"]},"fileAbsolutePath":"/home/28041/opensource/github.com/mmistakes/made-mistakes-gatsby/src/posts/mastering-paper/switching-tools.md"},"previous":{"frontmatter":{"path":"/procreate-paintings/april-c-portrait/","title":"Messy paint across the scalp","categories":["procreate-paintings"],"tags":["Procreate","portrait","illustration","Sktchy","time lapse"]},"fileAbsolutePath":"/home/28041/opensource/github.com/mmistakes/made-mistakes-gatsby/src/posts/procreate-paintings/april-c-portrait.md"}}}}